EnergyMonitoringApplicationService --> FilterEnergyReadingsCommand
EnergyMonitoringApplicationService --> EnergyReading

NotificationApplicationService --> AlertRepository
NotificationApplicationService --> CreateAlertCommand
NotificationApplicationService --> Alert

BillingApplicationService --> PlanRepository
BillingApplicationService --> SubscriptionRepository
