BillingApplicationService --> SubscribeCommand
BillingApplicationService --> Plan
BillingApplicationService --> Subscription

' =========================================================
' DOMAIN RELATIONSHIPS
' =========================================================

User "1" o-- "0..*" AccessProfile
AccessProfile "1" o-- "0..*" Permission

Device --> DeviceType
Device --> DeviceStatus
Routine --> RoutineAction
Routine --> Device : references deviceId
EnergyReading --> Device : references deviceId
Alert --> AlertLevel
Alert --> Device : references deviceId

Plan --> PlanCode
Plan "1" o-- "0..*" PlanFeature
Subscription --> PlanCode
Subscription --> SubscriptionStatus
Subscription --> Plan : references planId
Subscription --> User : references userId

